{
  "title": "Richly Spiced Vietnamese Chicken Curry",
  "description": "A citrusy and molten Vietnamese dish featuring ghee and tandoor spices, perfect for a weeknight dinner, this recipe is ayurvedic-rajasic-friendly and serves 4 people",
  "cuisine": "Vietnamese",
  "diet": [
    "gluten-free",
